overview:
Andre Taylor is the founder of iDidGo (Tripenvy) an organically generated travel network that provides real reviews created by real people, while connecting users to one another based on the same travel agenda.

Ididgo’s beta version was released privately on October 10th 2012 and currently still in development.

Andre born in Spanish Town Jamaica and has lived in Toronto, Knoxville Tennessee, Boston Massachusetts and London England. The travel experience is the root of ididgo’s creation.

www.ididgo.com is a first venture for Andre Taylor.
